<% } %>

Rooms:
- [[Back Room]]

:: Back Room
<% if (!s.key) { %>
Items:
- <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="key-item">Pick up key</a>
<% } else { %>
There is nothing here.
<% } %>

<%
$(function() {
	$('.key-item').click(function() {
		s.key = true;
		$(this).replaceWith('<span>You have a key.</span>');
	});
});
%>

Rooms:
- [[Front Room]]

:: Exit
You found the key and went through the door!
